{"tid":805104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[毒得過啟德、天津]委員反對收回高球場　「累積大量毒素要等70年」","createTime":"2018-09-03T13:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T15:37:25.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5cd6ec65b0a8717e5b93a31589199d7907e7a3e1","tid":805104,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T13:47:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180903/58641118\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180903%2F58641118&d=plTPkCoj89AXc0oqNvzSRF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=73a32923\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180903%2F58641118&h=b1af6517\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180903/58641118</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為期5個月的土地大辯論公眾諮詢，將於本月底結束，土地供應專責小組主席黃遠輝，今晚出席港區省級政協委員聯誼會的土地諮詢會。席間委員踴躍發言，多人表示支持填海方案，反對回收粉嶺高球場。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">西安政協黎炎錫指</span>，高球場已有過百年歷史，有保留價值，而且農藥、疏水等設施已令土地累積大量毒素，要改為建屋土地相信要50至70年</strong>；另外有委員指，中國在南沙建人工島只需一年，相信新的建築技術可加快填海造地的過程。<br />\n<br />\n黃遠輝回應指，填海是中長期造地方案，需要15至20年才有樓落成，就算社會上很多人支持填海，這只可視之為中長期方案，香港現時土地及房屋問題非常迫切，仍需要研究一些短期可行的增加土地方案。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n毒得過啟德、天津?啟德停機坪機油 + 油庫、工場機油都住緊人啦，再勁d睇下天津大爆炸，沒事兒沒事兒幾年啦on9"},{"pid":"0cb7d95155bdda50eeb7fd5a8ab3c3173dc1e3c8","tid":805104,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T13:58:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309d9804c9880405292f8361da1b2cd0aa5f9ccf","tid":805104,"uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T14:40:49.000Z","msg":"政協通常都係智障 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\